  "description": "AutoPulse at maximum rate with full accent — the pulse system has gone haywire, firing subdivisions at speeds the visualizer cannot track. Scanlines overloading, feedback loop running near saturation. The zero-audio identity becomes a cascade of visual artifacts: the synthesizer is a TV receiving nothing, broadcasting everything.",
